    "causal_summary": "Plan the Deep Alignment shadow-parity harness for migration to the typed event-ledger substrate. The harness runs the new ledger path beside the legacy emitter, compares canonical events and public projections event-for-event, and blocks any authority cutover until parity, replay determinism, and fail-closed mismatch handling are green. It consumes the phase-011 shadow framework and reuses the shared review-loop contract frozen in phase 009.",
